OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,FGlasgow Central station will remain
OL,7,Fclosed throughout Tuesday and is
OL,8,Fexpected to undergo safety inspections
OL,9,Ffollowing the devastating fire at an
OL,10,Fadjacent building.
OL,12,FRail operators have warned that
OL,13,Fdisruption is expected to continue for
OL,14,Fa number of days after Scotland's
OL,15,Fbusiest station was closed throughout
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,18,FAll services to and from the station
OL,19,Fhave been suspended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
