OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773169064
OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,FThe fire began in a vape shop on Union
OL,7,FStreet, before the flames spread
OL,8,Fthrough the building and around the
OL,9,Fcorner on to Gordon Street.
OL,11,FOnly the facade of the building has
OL,12,Fbeen left standing on Gordon Street.
OL,14,FNetwork Rail has confirmed the station
OL,15,Fwill remain closed on Tuesday.
OL,17,FWhile Central Station itself is
OL,18,Fthought to have escaped any major
OL,19,Fdamage, the impact of the firefighting
OL,20,Fefforts and the intense heat of the
OL,21,Fblaze is likely to require assessment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
