OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Network Rail said
OL,7,Fon Monday: "While the fire is now
OL,8,Funder control, emergency services are
OL,9,Fstill on site and we continue to
OL,10,Fsupport their response.
OL,12,F"The station will remain closed today
OL,13,Fand tomorrow.
OL,15,F"Timescales for reopening will only be
OL,16,Fconfirmed once we are able to safely
OL,17,Fgain access and carry out the
OL,18,Fnecessary checks.
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
