OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,F"All services to and from Glasgow
OL,7,FCentral are currently suspended, and
OL,8,Fpassengers should continue to follow
OL,9,Falternative travel arrangements as
OL,10,Fadvised by their train operators."
OL,12,FScotRail said disruption is likely to
OL,13,Fcontinue for several days.
OL,15,FDavid Ross, ScotRail chief operating
OL,16,Fofficer, said: "We'd like to thank our
OL,17,Fcolleagues in the fire and emergency
OL,18,Fservices who worked incredibly hard to
OL,19,Ftackle the blaze and prevent it from
OL,20,Fspreading to the station itself.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]xD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
