PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773169064
OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,F"We know this closure will cause
OL,7,Fsignificant disruption for our
OL,8,Fcustomers, and we're very sorry for
OL,9,Fthe impact this will have on their
OL,10,Fjourneys."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, more than #80,000 has been
OL,13,Fraised to support a number of
OL,14,Fbusinesses which were destroyed in the
OL,15,Fblaze.
OL,17,FThe crowdfunding platform GoFundMe
OL,18,Fsaid the sum had been raised for six
OL,19,Ffirms which lost their premises in the
OL,20,Fblaze.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]
