OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,FThey included a hairdressing salon run
OL,7,Fby Joe Diaz, who fled the building
OL,8,Fwhen the fire began to take hold on
OL,9,FSunday.
OL,11,FHe told the Press Association how he
OL,12,Fand his partner encountered "really
OL,13,Fheavy, dark smoke" as they fled the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,FMr Diaz said: "We just got our client
OL,17,Fand said, let's just run and get out
OL,18,Fof here as soon as we can."
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@RO]xD@OOUzD@[O]
