OL,3,CGlasgow Central to remain closed as
OL,4,Crail disruption expected to continue
OL,6,FA passer-by, Lamin Kongira, tried to
OL,7,Fextinguish the blaze in a vape shop on
OL,8,FSunday, but was forced back by an
OL,9,F"explosion" from within the premises.
OL,11,FHe described hearing another more
OL,12,Fpowerful blast shortly afterwards.
OL,14,FAvanti West Coast advised passengers
OL,15,Fthat an amended train service will run
OL,16,Fto Preston, Carlisle and Motherwell,
OL,17,F"enabling customers to connect with
OL,18,Ftrains to Edinburgh and local services
OL,19,Fto the Glasgow area".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]yD@AOU{D@TO]
